\c 7
\s Jehovha anotsvaka kururama
\p
\v 1 Zvino negore rechina ramambo Dhariyasi shoko raJehovha rakasvika kuna Zekariya nezuva rechina romwedzi wepfumbamwe, iwo weKisirevhi.
\v 2 Zvino vanhu veBheteri vakange vatuma Sharezeri naRegemimereki, navanhu vavo, ku\add ndo\add*kumbira nyasha kuna Jehovha,
\v 3 nokutaura navapristi veimba yaJehovha wehondo navaporofita, vachiti: Ko ndochema nomwedzi wechishanu, ndichizviparadzanisa navamwe, sezvandaiita makore awa mazhinji here?
\p
\v 4 Ipapo shoko raJehovha wehondo rakasvika kwandiri, richiti:
\v 5 Taura navanhu vese venyika ino, navapristi, uti: Zvamaitsanya muchichema nomwedzi wechishanu nowechinomwe, makore ano anamakumi manomwe, maitongotsanya nokuda kwangu, nokuda kwangu here?
\v 6 Kana muchidya, kana muchimwa, hamuzvidyiri nokuzvimwira here?
\v 7 Ko haasi mashoko aJehovha aakadanidzira navaporofita vakare, Jerusarema richakagarwa navanhu richinomufaro, iro namaguta aro ese akaripoteredza, nenyika yechamhembe yenyika yamapani dzichina vanhu.
\p
\v 8 Zvino shoko raJehovha rakasvika kuna Zekariya, richiti:
\v 9 Ndizvo zvakataura Jehovha wehondo, achiti: Ruramisirai kwazvo pakutonga, umwe neumwe aitire hama yake unyoro netsitsi;
\v 10 regai kumanikidza chirikadzi, kana nherera, kana mutorwa, kana murombo; kurege kuva neumwe wenyu anofungira hama yake zvakaipa pamwoyo pake.
\v 11 Asi vakaramba kuteerera, vakabvisa fudzi ravo, nokudzivira nzeve dzavo kuti varege kunzwa.
\v 12 Zvirokwazvo, mwoyo yavo vakaiita sedhaimani, kuti varege kunzwa murairo namashoko akatumwa naJehovha wehondo noMweya wake navaporofita vakare; saka kutsamwa kukuru kwakabuda kuna Jehovha wehondo.
\v 13 Zvino sezvaakadana, ivo vakaramba kunzwa, saizvozvo ivo vachadanawo ini ndicharamba kunzwa ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha wehondo;
\v 14 asi ndichavaparadzira nechamupupuri pakati pendudzi dzese dzavakange vasingazivi. Nokuti nyika yakava dongo shure kwavo, kukasava nomunhu akaenda kana kudzoka neko; nokuti vakaparadza nyika yakange ichifadza.